{"tid":2084092,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[一息尚存］七月一維園見！！！！","createTime":"2020-06-29T06:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:26:42.000Z","uid":98884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e4574d5b8130612ca41b70cade53aa4a7f0465","tid":2084092,"uid":98884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:19:24.000Z","msg":"七月一維園見！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ew5LhHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEw5LhHh.jpg&h=a38fc331&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NK1njVD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNK1njVD.jpg&h=62ac9fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEH9Kni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEH9Kni.jpg&h=a60a48ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00532ecbbf58238f90035a635519f9f236b19dc4","tid":2084092,"uid":98884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"一人一post推71<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388871f20dd6e0ac717cc304f5585db748f9ffc8","tid":2084092,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"你哋班連登仔， 喺連登圍爐洗版有撚用？<br />\n<br />\n我要見到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IG Facebook</span>  各大社交平台<br />\n都要見到呢幾隻字<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>7月1 維園見</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d9f29ac9a246d036617aa32ac6152c62459434a7","tid":2084092,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:22:12.000Z","msg":"手足大家71見<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=cc7f9dd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"390e12f0b976dd226907cbc788bcf30507d2b827","tid":2084092,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"【置頂】<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>選戰告急</strong></span></span> 倒數十星期 立即十星期拉票行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2082608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2082608</a>"}]}